@Next "P-USER8"
@Prev "P-USER6"
@Toc "Par"

USER7=scriptname
================

This specifies the name of an ARexx script to run when F7 is pressed.

There is no default script.


@EndNode

@Node "P-USER8" "MPMorph.guide/P-USER8"
@Next "P-USER9"
@Prev "P-USER7"
@Toc "Par"

USER8=scriptname
================

This specifies the name of an ARexx script to run when F8 is pressed.

There is no default script.


@EndNode

