@Node "Bugs" "MPMorph.guide/Bugs"
@Next "ToDo"
@Prev "Errors"
@Toc "Main"

Known (and unknown errors)
**************************

   @{b}*@{ub} Known Problems

        @{b}*@{ub} The docs are sparse in places and are probably incorrect as
          well!

        @{b}*@{ub} Unsaved project does not check that gadgets really have been
          edited.

        @{b}*@{ub} This guide sometimes has very long lines. Also @{b}bold@{ub} items
          following @{b}*@{ub} are followed by too many spaces.  This appears to
          be due to a problem with MakeInfo, menus and lists.

        @{b}*@{ub} This guide may not look correct when using amigaguide.library
          versions before 40. This will not be fixed.

        @{b}*@{ub} Sizing EGS windows from the top or left may corrupt the
          display. I believe this an EGS problem.

        @{b}*@{ub} MPRender is not yet localized.

        @{b}*@{ub} When moving or sizing an image window sometimes lines can be
          drawn twice, clearing the lines. Closing and reopening will
          redraw correctly.

        @{b}*@{ub} It takes a long time to open a Public Screen - ObtainPen??

   @{b}*@{ub} Unknown Problems?

        @{b}*@{ub} None at present.

Please report any other bugs by EMail to mark@topic.demon.co.uk or
mpaddock@cix.compulink.co.uk.


@EndNode

