***********************************

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 4.8

        @{b}*@{ub} MPRender now uses COLOURS parameter.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added full .html docs.

        @{b}*@{ub} Spelling mistakes and version fixed in MPImage.library.

        @{b}*@{ub} Reordered MPMorph catalog for easier localisation.

        @{b}*@{ub} Updated bugs.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added TODO list.

        @{b}*@{ub} Noted WWW support page.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 4.7

        @{b}*@{ub} Fixed enforcer hit in MPRender.

        @{b}*@{ub} Updated algorithms to indicate memory usage.

        @{b}*@{ub} Corrected version in Install script.

        @{b}*@{ub} Updated install script for cjpeg/djpeg to match standard
          usage.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 4.6

        @{b}*@{ub} New version of MPGui.library which should work if opened more
          than once.

        @{b}*@{ub} New version of MPImage.library.??? which fixes SaveMPImage()
          bug.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 4.5

        @{b}*@{ub} Fixed IndexHelp.MPM to work correctly

        @{b}*@{ub} New versions of libraries and tools which open
          locale.library(38) to work on OS3.0.

        @{b}*@{ub} New version of MPImage.library.??? which fixes enforcer hit.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 4.4

        @{b}*@{ub} Bug fixes.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added CTRL-C checking to MPMorph and MPRender.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added RTPreview script (USER4).

        @{b}*@{ub} Added LastUpdate to Rexx GetAttr.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added Saved to Rexx SetAttr.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added COPY/S to Rexx SaveAs

        @{b}*@{ub} Renumbed some catalog message - some work still to be done.

        @{b}*@{ub} Updated some scripts.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added NOPROGRESS to MPRENDER.

        @{b}*@{ub} Added PROGRESSHOOK to MPRENDER.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 4.3

        @{b}*@{ub} Loads of changes. Following is only partial.

        @{b}*@{ub} Renamed MPMorph/MPRender

        @{b}*@{ub} Faster rendering.

        @{b}*@{ub} Removed render settings from MPMorph.

        @{b}*@{ub} Reordered some MPMorph menus.

        @{b}*@{ub} Guis by MPGui.library.

        @{b}*@{ub} Image loading/saving by MPImage.library.

        @{b}*@{ub} Sysihack compatible.

        @{b}*@{ub} OS3.0+ only.

        @{b}*@{ub} Scaled menu checks and Amiga keys.

        @{b}*@{ub} Open recent files.

        @{b}*@{ub} Two preferences editors/settings files.

        @{b}*@{ub} Full ARexx interface.

        @{b}*@{ub} Scales input images.


@EndNode

@Node "Hints" "MPMorph.guide/Hints"
@Next "Distribution"
@Prev "History"
@Toc "Main"

Hints & Tips
************

This section supplies some hopefully useful information which may not
be immediately apparent elsewhere.

@{b}Speed?@{ub}

If you do not have an FPU then set the INTEGER parameter to YES.  Even
if you do have an FPU this may still make things run faster.

If it still slow then try changing DX and DY to 1 (or more).

If you have lots of memory then setting the precalculate part of MODE
should help.

@{b}What MODE?@{ub}

This depends on the type of Morph.

If you are, say, rotating some text on a background, then it is
probably best to set the stationary part. You would NOT want to set the
precalculate once part.

If you are morphing, say, two faces where the points do not move much
between the first and last image then it may be best to set the
precalculate part (provided you have enough free memory). Setting the
Delaunay part may also be a good idea.

Setting search is probably not a good idea.

@{b}Not enough memory for MPMorph@{ub}

If you run out of Chip memory when trying to load large images then try
setting ZOOM to OFF.


@EndNode

